      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/goldman-raises-global-equities-overweight-economic-growth-prospects-2024-02-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鉴于经济增长和制造业活动复苏的前景，高盛将全球股市评级上调至“增持”，此前高盛对资产的评级为“中性”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/goldman-raises-global-equities-overweight-economic-growth-prospects-2024-02-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:27:32 GMT</pubDate>
